{"tid":2008490,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"尖沙咀酒店走廊遺懷疑可卡因粉末　警方檢走調查","createTime":"2020-05-09T05:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T05:42:10.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"078e328951450d9c5d76b3c4be0ec3d69669c233","tid":2008490,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:33:32.000Z","msg":"周六（9日）凌晨零時許，警方接獲尖沙咀彌敦道118至130號某酒店經理報案，他指有住客在某樓層走廊，發現1包可疑白色粉末。警員趕抵調查後，懷疑該包粉末為可卡因毒品，重約0.6克，事後將其檢走調查。警方正追查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4bab52e66518985dbf5dccd1bbe318b91e0250","tid":2008490,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"[行動po] 聽日尖咀見 多你一個就係多<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2008475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2008475</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"22e2e259ee9e4896e777fd6f3da29266b31df6e4","tid":2008490,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"又交戲想洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eccd45254dbd9049dd404961ef70cac1577c58f","tid":2008490,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}